      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Paper money representing standard monetary units in the United States, Canada, Australia, New Zealand, historically from states in the USA, and other places; each equal to 100 cents. Originally from a silver coin that circulated in many European countries.</Note_Text>
